        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="REPEAT"><a href="#REPEAT" class="headerlink" title="REPEAT"></a>REPEAT</h1><pre><code><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">repeat </span><br><span class="line">until condition </span><br><span class="line">end repeat;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></code></pre><h1 id="LOOP"><a href="#LOOP" class="headerlink" title="LOOP"></a>LOOP</h1><pre><code><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">c:loop</span><br><span class="line">if condition then </span><br><span class="line">leave c;</span><br><span class="line">end if;</span><br><span class="line">end loop c;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></code></pre><ul><li>Top| Limit | OFFSET | IS NULL | &lt;&gt;(不匹配)</li></ul><h2 id="通配符"><a href="#通配符" class="headerlink" title="通配符"></a>通配符</h2><ul><li><p>‘.*%’ | ‘_‘ | ‘[]’</p></li><li><p>Concat(a,b) | R/LTRIM() | YEAR()</p></li><li><p>子查询单列</p></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
