        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="存储过程和存储函数"><a href="#存储过程和存储函数" class="headerlink" title="存储过程和存储函数"></a>存储过程和存储函数</h1><ul><li><p>减少应用程序和内存的交互，提高数据处理效率  </p></li><li><p>创建存储函数  </p><pre><code><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">create procedure precedure_name ([proc_parameter[...]])</span><br><span class="line">begin</span><br><span class="line"> SQL Sequence</span><br><span class="line">end;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></code></pre></li><li><p>分隔符声明  </p>  <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">delimiter symbol</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>调用存储过程  </p>  <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">call procedure_name()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>查看存储过程  </p>  <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">select name from mysql.proc where db = &#x27;db_name&#x27;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">show procedure status;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">show create procedure test.pro_test1 \G ; </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>删除存储过程  </p>  <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">drop procedure prodecure_name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h1 id="变量"><a href="#变量" class="headerlink" title="变量"></a>变量</h1><ul><li>declear   <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">declear var_name[,...] type default default_value;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>set    <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">set var_name = &#x27;var_name&#x27;;</span><br><span class="line">select var_name;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">select count(*) into var_name from table;</span><br><span class="line">select var_name;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>if  <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">if search_condition then statement_list  </span><br><span class="line">[elseif search_condition then statement]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">end if;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>传递函数    <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">create procedure procedure_name([in/out/inout])</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">call precedure_name(value, @variable_name)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><ul><li>case    <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">case case_value</span><br><span class="line">when when_value then statement_list</span><br><span class="line">end case;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">case</span><br><span class="line">when search_condition then statement_list</span><br><span class="line">end case;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>while    <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">while search_condiiton do </span><br><span class="line">statement_list</span><br><span class="line">end while;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
