      <title>Summer_Plan</title>
      <link href="/2021/06/22/06-22/"/>
      <url>/2021/06/22/06-22/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Summer-Plan"><a href="#Summer-Plan" class="headerlink" title="Summer Plan"></a>Summer Plan</h2><ul><li>租房问题(水电费、地铁站远近、大型超市、通风、光线、预付押金、租期、合租情况、网络电缆、空调卫生间)</li><li>实习问题(大致确定世环的时间、寻找成都、上海类似工作)</li><li>竞赛问题(kaggle比赛学习<em>熟悉竞赛流程、寻找合适比赛、队友</em> 、tianci竞赛、 建模竞赛、英语竞赛)</li><li>论文问题(仿写小论文、 实验室老师相关论文<strong>确定以后大致方向</strong>、关注领域论文动态，大致复原五篇左右文献)</li><li>旅游问题(重庆、太原、绵阳、老家贷款问题)</li></ul><h2 id="Star-Sensor-Based-Satellite-Attitude-Attitude-Rate-Estimator-1985"><a href="#Star-Sensor-Based-Satellite-Attitude-Attitude-Rate-Estimator-1985" class="headerlink" title="Star-Sensor-Based Satellite Attitude/Attitude Rate Estimator  1985"></a>Star-Sensor-Based Satellite Attitude/Attitude Rate Estimator  1985</h2><h3 id="Introduction"><a href="#Introduction" class="headerlink" title="Introduction"></a>Introduction</h3><p>on-orbit attitude rate determination’s problems </p><ul><li>sensitivity limitations</li><li>bandwidth limitations</li></ul><ul><li>gyroscope(attitude and attitude rate determination)</li><li>stellar inertial systems</li></ul><p>CCD/CID  contribute to on-orbit attitude determination and control systems based solely on star sensor measurements</p><ul><li><p>low attitude dynamics <em>gyroloss attitude determination</em> | <em>control systems</em><br>Applications &gt; meteorology | Earth resources | communications</p></li><li><p>high-accuracy mission <strong>three-axis-stablized zero-momentum-bias designs</strong>  </p><ol><li>the principal axes’ independent control to supplyment the system’s inherent neutral stability  </li><li>gyroscopic stiffness is sacrificed to permit high bandwidth control about all three spacecraft axes  </li><li>0.5Hz bandwidth attitude rate information to provide adequete stability</li></ol></li></ul><h2 id="Filter-Derivation"><a href="#Filter-Derivation" class="headerlink" title="Filter Derivation"></a>Filter Derivation</h2>]]></content>
      
      
